text.section:
On the 1st day of each regular session of the General Assembly, the Secretary of Budget and Management shall submit, subject to § 2-1246 of the State Government Article, to the appropriate committees of the General Assembly a report that:
states the total number of additional staff positions for which the Board of Public Works has given approval since the last regular session; and
for each position, states:
the type;
the salary or wages; and
the reasons for the approval.
